    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> pepper strips</strong> and the <strong>remaining Cajun-style spice mix </strong>and cook for 8-10 min or until starting to soften</p>",
